## Context
DevOps review: every test file repeats
`sys.path.insert(0, .../tickets/tools)`. This is fragile — new test
files must copy the incantation. Should use conftest.py or
pyproject.toml pythonpath.

## Actions
1. Add tests/conftest.py with the sys.path insert
2. Remove the sys.path lines from individual test files
3. Or: add tickets/tools to [tool.pytest.ini_options] pythonpath

## Exit criteria
- New test files can import ticket_parser without sys.path hacks
- Existing tests still pass
